com.konakartadmin.bl

Class ExecuteBatchDirectEE

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.konakartadmin.bl.KKBatchBase
      • com.konakartadmin.bl.ExecuteBatchDirectEE

  • public class ExecuteBatchDirectEE
extends KKBatchBase
    This is a utility for running batch jobs outside the Quartz environment. It uses the execute interface on the KKAdminIf engine.
